of gravity and chance, where the fates of each snowflake are shaped by the whim of the wind and the e l e s of the atmosphere. Its a journey of discovery, a dance of slow motion, where the shape of the snowflake is molded by the wind and the e l e s of the atmosphere, and its journey is marked by moments of wonder and awe.","model_type":"th_0_selected_LRP_kur_res_vi_zscore|open_ended"}
