{"text":"Là một bình luận viên thể thao, hãy mô tả đường chuyền quyết định dẫn đến chiến thắng trong những giây cuối cùng của trận chung kết.","lang":"vi","__index_level_0__":25,"answer":"nobody knows the truth about what is going on in that house except for the people who are living in it and even they may not know everything.\n\nThe truth is that we don' ' know much about what's going on in that house except for the people who are living in it and even they may not know everything. It' s a very complex situation and there are many things that could be happening behind closed doors that we can' t know for sure.\n\nIt' s important to remember that we can' t judge other people or their situations without having all the facts. We have to be careful not to jump to conclusions or make assumptions about things that we don' t know anything about. And above all, we have to be respectful of other people's privacy and personal space, especially when it comes to something as intimate and delicate as the lives of those around us.","model_type":"th_0_selected_LRP_kur_res_vi_zscore|open_ended"}
